ZH: 他留下来帮助我。
EN: He stayed behind to help me.

ZH: 父母每次出去都会留给我钱。
EN: My parents always leave me money when they go out.

ZH: 我想留在家里度过这个周末。
EN: I want to stay at home and spend this weekend.

ZH: 请你留意一下这个细节。
EN: Please pay attention to this detail.

ZH: 过马路要留神。
EN: Be careful when crossing the road.

ZH: 我们打算明年留学去美国。
EN: We plan to study abroad in the United States next year.

ZH: 他们决定临时留在这里开会。
EN: They decided to stay here temporarily for a meeting.

ZH: 请留个位子给老人。
EN: Please save a seat for the elderly.

ZH: 我们应该留住这个优秀员工。
EN: We should retain this excellent employee.

ZH: 让我给你留一个好印象。
EN: Let me leave a good impression on you.

ZH: 忘了关灯，你可以留着。
EN: Forget to turn off the lights, you can leave it on.

ZH: 我在车站留下了我的钱包。
EN: I left my wallet at the train station.

ZH: 祝你在新的工作中留下好印象。
EN: I wish you good impression at your new job.

ZH: 她留下了一封信，说明她不会回来了。
EN: She left a letter explaining that she wouldn't come back.

ZH: 给我留点面试的时间，我需要做准备。
EN: Leave me some time for the interview, I need to prepare.

ZH: 没人愿意留在一个不友好的环境里。
EN: No one wants to stay in an unfriendly environment.

ZH: 他们打算留下来继续参观这个城市。
EN: They plan to stay and continue exploring this city.

ZH: 这个问题给了我留下深刻的印象。
EN: This problem left me with a deep impression.

ZH: 麻烦你留意一下这位客人。
EN: Could you please pay attention to this guest?

ZH: 如果你现在留下来，我们可以更早出发。
EN: If you stay now, we can leave earlier.
